reetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2008-07-27a.png?fit=758%2C988&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-28484 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2008-07-27a.png?resize=758%2C987&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"987\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2008-07-27a.png?w=1342&amp;ssl=1 1342w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2008-07-27a.png?resize=230%2C300&amp;ssl=1 230w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2008-07-27a.png?resize=786%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 786w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2008-07-27a.png?resize=768%2C1000&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/2008-07-27a.png?resize=1179%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 1179w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"19953\" data-permalink=\"https://estreetshuffle.com/2008-07-27b/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2008-07-27b.png?fit=962%2C1748&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"962,1748\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"2008-07-27b\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2008-07-27b.png?fit=165%2C300&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2008-07-27b.png?fit=564%2C1024&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-19953 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2008-07-27b.png?resize=758%2C1377&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"758\" height=\"1377\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2008-07-27b.png?w=962&amp;ssl=1 962w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2008-07-27b.png?resize=165%2C300&amp;ssl=1 165w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2008-07-27b.png?resize=564%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 564w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2008-07-27b.png?resize=768%2C1395&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/estreetshuffle.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/2008-07-27b.png?resize=845%2C1536&amp;ssl=1 845w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 758px) 100vw, 758px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>2012:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the band play their first of two spectacular shows in Gothenburg, featuring tour premieres of &#8220;Drive All Night&#8221; and &#8220;Girls in Their Summer Clothes.&#8221;</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/uDZBeKRUa9M?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/r8qpTL1wxGQ?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/geACCnafymo?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2013:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band wrap up the European Wrecking Ball Tour with two shows in Nolan Park in Kilkenny, Ireland. On Night One, the festivities begin early, with Josh Ritter, Damien Dempsey, and Glen Hansard playing opening sets. After Bruce takes the stage to &#8220;This Little Light of Mine,&#8221; he follows with a long set that includes a full album performance of <em>Born in the U.S.A.</em>, the tour premieres of &#8220;Shake&#8221; and &#8220;Sweet Soul Music&#8221; and a rare outing for &#8220;Stand On It.&#8221; Glen Hansard returns to the stage to perform &#8220;Drive All Night&#8221; with Bruce.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/wGX9t5Tehjs?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/sMLYEWucWm8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/vPwOurNpVx8?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Bbd2eFZnONA?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/IWHuWlYEuxM?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p><strong>2018:\u00a0</strong>Patti is absent, but\u00a0<em>Springsteen on Broadway</em> continues its theatrical run at the Walter Kerr Theater in New York City nevertheless. Bruce plays his &#8220;B&#8221; set as a result, swapping in &#8220;Long Time Comin'&#8221; and &#8220;This Hard Land&#8221; for the customary duets. The show takes a two week hiatus after tonight.</p>\n<p><strong>2024:\u00a0</strong>Bruce and the E Street Band close out their European tour with a second night at Wembley Stadium in London that features a guest appearance by Patti Scialfa.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/p6syv7Jy4w4?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent&#038;listType=playlist&#038;list=RDp6syv7Jy4w4\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>Happy birthday, Cindy Mizelle! Also on this date: Bruce sues Mike Appel, plays the first &#8220;Candy&#8217;s Room&#8221; in 15 years, duets with Glen Hansard, and more.</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 57876, "comment_status": "open", "ping_status": "open", "sticky": false, "template": "", "format": "standard", "meta": {"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_active": false, "_monsterinsights_sitenote_note": "", "_monsterinsights_sitenote_category": 0, "jetpack_post_was_ever_published": false, "_jetpack_newsletter_access": "", "_jetpack_dont_email_post_to_subs": f